| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6433 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6181017e-f83c-5eaa-8b9c-ac6234c6ca67"
